.name
CyroUtils
.author
Cyrogenic Software 
.description
Four handy animation utilities from Cryogenic Software.  Includes an
animation creation tool that allows you to combine selected pictures into a
standard animation, an animation information tool that is used to extract
certain information from a given animation, an animation combining tool
that allows you to join two animations into a larger one, and an animation
splitting tool that allows you to split one animation into two smaller
ones.  
